合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下</span><br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLBJubU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLBJubU.jpg&h=dba2aa56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推呀屌你再過20個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n聽日要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"0475e5d1a94209d42d97de209a244ebe7d18a66a","tid":1776830,"uid":213163,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T20:27:42.000Z","msg":"Wtsapp都可以傾公事㗎啫<br />\n我成日都唔覆機 但好愛男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都睇漏msg<br />\n你哋坦誠溝通下 將你嘅擔心同佢講可能會好啲呢"},{"pid":"2bc7c1ee0ad5f70ce8a6073ab2c2181308487cb0","tid":1776830,"uid":289111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"913c68e80db90069db90a53f86decc1c9ebfa9bb","tid":1776830,"uid":285514,"like":4,"dislike":33,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T20:16:30.000Z","msg":"男朋友online但唔覆機嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n我先，唔係嘛咁鬼易...<br />\n去咗廁所<br />\n<br />\n下一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T20:28:21.000Z","msg":"咁會啦 去成5、6個鐘廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d77b1823b5dd6a4ee39633b611a74f371a17ed7","tid":1776830,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bc7c1ee0ad5f70ce8a6073ab2c2181308487cb0","tid":1776830,"uid":289111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"913c68e80db90069db90a53f86decc1c9ebfa9bb","tid":1776830,"uid":285514,"like":4,"dislike":33,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T20:16:30.000Z","msg":"男朋友online但唔覆機嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n我先，唔係嘛咁鬼易...<br />\n去咗廁所<br />\n